        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Resist Executive Amnesty on Defense Installations Act or the READI Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of a military installation to house an alien who is unlawfully present in the United States or undergoing removal proceedings. </p>]]>
        </text>
